data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: The protagonist of this picture is a young Caucasian lady in her uniform. She has blonde hair and a typical Caucasian look, and she is standing there with her arms crossed. She wears a white shirt and a black apron, and she is looking at something in distance. There are glasses and while bottles surrounding her, and there are some groups of people standing behind her. It looks like the lady is at work in a bar and is waiting for customers to purchase some liquor.
